we are right now.

266
00:16:07.662 --> 00:16:09.012
Oh.

267
00:16:09.142 --> 00:16:10.882
I mean. it's gotta be
worse for them. right?

268
00:16:11.013 --> 00:16:13.843
Not knowing.

269
00:16:13.973 --> 00:16:15.453
Just...

270
