poor man's potato vodka.

338
00:20:17.128 --> 00:20:19.038
You're one of the guys
from the two cars. huh?

339
00:20:22.133 --> 00:20:25.143
Your. uh. friend. uh--
friend got. uh...

340
00:20:25.267 --> 00:20:27.837
Yeah. Yeah.

341
00:20:27.965 --> 00:20:31.185
Look. if it's
any consolation. it--

342
00:20:31.317 --> 00:20:33.487
it gets easier. man.
it really does.

343
00:20:34.929 --> 00:20:37.889
Gets easier.
that's rich.

344
00:20:38.019 --> 00:20:39.719
That is fucking rich.

345
00:20:42.371 --> 00:20:46.161
You know. you guys are--
you're like rats in a maze.

346
00:20:46.288 --> 00:20:50.598
