How do we get out of here?

352
00:21:13.141 --> 00:21:15.621
'Cause unless we
know where "here" is.

353
00:21:15.752 --> 00:21:17.062
we can't get outta here.

354
00:21:17.188 --> 00:21:20.058
It's like-- it's like... this.
it's like. uh.

355
00:21:20.191 --> 00:21:22.111
